---
// src/pages/aitha-pm-how-it-works.astro
// Aitha PM — Full pitch page: how it works, for residential and commercial
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>How Aitha PM Works — AI Property Management Communication | TaskRocket</title>
  <meta name="description" content="A full walkthrough of how Aitha PM handles tenant calls, voicemail triage, vendor dispatch, and compliance documentation — for residential and commercial property managers." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --parchment: #F5EFE1;
      --ink: #1B1A17;
      --brass: #B08B3E;
      --teal: #2DD4BF;
      --orange: #FF7A30;
      --navy: #101828;
      --rule: rgba(27,26,23,0.10);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; background: var(--parchment); color: var(--ink); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; }

    /* NAV */
    nav { padding: 18px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); background: var(--parchment); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
    .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px; }
    .nav-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .nav-brand { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-brand span { color: var(--teal); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(27,26,23,0.55); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--ink); }
    .nav-cta { background: var(--navy); color: #fff !important; padding: 9px 20px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600 !important; }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: #1d2e47 !important; }

    /* HERO */
    .hero { background: var(--navy); padding: 80px 0 72px; }
    .hero-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .hero h1 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(36px, 4.5vw, 56px); font-weight: 700; color: #F5EFE1; line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 22px; }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--brass); }
    .hero-desc { font-size: 18px; color: rgba(245,239,225,0.65); max-width: 640px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-primary { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 28px; background: var(--teal); color: var(--navy); border-radius: 8px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #1D9E75; color: #fff; }
    .btn-ghost { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 14px 22px; color: rgba(245,239,225,0.7); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,239,225,0.2); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { color: #F5EFE1; border-color: rgba(245,239,225,0.5); }

    /* SECTIONS */
    .section { padding: 80px 0; }
    .section-white { padding: 80px 0; background: #fff; }
    .section-navy { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--navy); }
    .section-parchment { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--parchment); }
    .eyebrow { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--brass); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .eyebrow-teal { color: var(--teal); }
    h2 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 40px); font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    h2 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--brass); }
    h2.light { color: #F5EFE1; }
    .lead { font-size: 17px; color: rgba(27,26,23,0.6); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .lead.light { color: rgba(245,239,225,0.6); }

    /* FLOW STEPS */
    .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
    .step-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr; gap: 0 24px; position: relative; padding-bottom: 40px; }
    .step-row:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }
    .step-row:last-child .step-line { display: none; }
    .step-num-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
    .step-num { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy); color: #F5EFE1; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .step-line { width: 2px; flex: 1; background: var(--rule); margin-top: 8px; }
    .step-content { padding-top: 10px; }
    .step-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .step-desc { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(27,26,23,0.6); line-height: 1.65; }

    /* PATH CARDS */
    .paths { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .path-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--rule); border-top: 4px solid var(--brass); padding: 24px 22px; }
    .path-card.red { border-top-color: #DC2626; }
    .path-card.blue { border-top-color: #378ADD; }
    .path-card.green { border-top-color: #639922; }
    .path-card.amber { border-top-color: var(--brass); }
    .path-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .path-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .path-desc { font-size: 13.5px; color: rgba(27,26,23,0.6); line-height: 1.6; }

    /* DASHBOARD MOCKUP */
    .dashboard-shell {
      background: #0A1018;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .dash-topbar {
      background: #060C12;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }
    .dash-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .dash-dot.r { background: #FF5F57; } .dash-dot.y { background: #FEBC2E; } .dash-dot.g { background: #28C840; }
    .dash-url { margin-left: 12px; font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); font-family: monospace; }
    .dash-body { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr 300px; height: 480px; }
    .dash-sidebar {
      background: #060C12;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      padding: 16px 0;
    }
    .dash-brand { padding: 0 16px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .dash-brand-name { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #F5EFE1; }
    .dash-brand-sub { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal); margin-top: 2px; }
    .dash-live { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); margin-top: 6px; }
    .dash-live-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--teal); animation: pulse-d 2s infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse-d { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:.3} }
    .dash-nav-item { padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; border-left: 2px solid transparent; }
    .dash-nav-item.active { color: #F5EFE1; border-left-color: var(--teal); background: rgba(45,212,191,0.05); }
    .dash-nav-badge { background: var(--brass); color: #fff; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 8px; }
    .dash-main { background: #F5EFE1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }
    .dash-header { padding: 14px 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27,26,23,0.08); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .dash-header-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); }
    .dash-stats { display: flex; gap: 14px; }
    .dash-stat { text-align: center; }
    .dash-stat-num { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); line-height: 1; }
    .dash-stat-num.o { color: var(--orange); }
    .dash-stat-num.t { color: var(--teal); }
    .dash-stat-label { font-size: 9px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: rgba(27,26,23,0.4); margin-top: 2px; }
    .dash-filter { padding: 8px 18px; display: flex; gap: 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27,26,23,0.06); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .filter-pill { padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; border: 1px solid rgba(27,26,23,0.15); color: rgba(27,26,23,0.5); cursor: pointer; }
    .filter-pill.active { background: var(--navy); color: #F5EFE1; border-color: var(--navy); }
    .dash-incidents { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 10px 14px; }
    .inc { background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(27,26,23,0.07); border-left: 3px solid var(--brass); padding: 10px 12px; margin-bottom: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: box-shadow 0.15s; }
    .inc:hover { box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .inc.active { border-left-color: var(--teal); }
    .inc.red { border-left-color: #DC2626; }
    .inc.green { border-left-color: #639922; }
    .inc-row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .inc-title { font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); }
    .inc-meta { font-size: 10px; color: rgba(27,26,23,0.45); }
    .badge { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; white-space: nowrap; }
    .badge-red { background: #FEE2E2; color: #DC2626; }
    .badge-orange { background: #FEF3C7; color: #D97706; }
    .badge-teal { background: #CCFBF1; color: #0F766E; }
    .badge-green { background: #D1FAE5; color: #059669; }
    .badge-brass { background: #FEF9EC; color: #B08B3E; }

    /* DETAIL PANEL */
    .dash-detail { background: #fff; border-left: 1px solid rgba(27,26,23,0.08); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }
    .detail-hdr { padding: 12px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27,26,23,0.07); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .detail-type { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal); margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .detail-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .detail-meta { font-size: 10px; color: rgba(27,26,23,0.45); }
    .detail-body { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 12px 14px; }
    .convo-label { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(27,26,23,0.35); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .msg { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .msg-ts { font-size: 9px; color: rgba(27,26,23,0.3); margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .bubble { display: inline-block; max-width: 88%; padding: 7px 10px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.45; }
    .bubble.in { background: #F3F4F6; color: #1F2937; border-radius: 10px 10px 10px 2px; }
    .bubble.out { background: var(--navy); color: #F5EFE1; border-radius: 10px 10px 2px 10px; float: right; }
    .bubble.sys { background: #FEF9EC; color: var(--brass); border: 1px solid rgba(176,139,62,0.2); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 10px; display: block; width: 100%; text-align: center; }
    .msg.out-wrap { text-align: right; }
    .clearfix::after { content: ''; display: block; clear: both; }

    /* CONVO EXAMPLES */
    .convos { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .convo-card { background: var(--navy); border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; }
    .convo-card-header { padding: 16px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); }
    .convo-card-type { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal); margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .convo-card-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #F5EFE1; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .convo-card-meta { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(245,239,225,0.4); }
    .convo-card-body { padding: 16px 20px; }
    .cm { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .cm-ts { font-size: 9px; color: rgba(245,239,225,0.25); margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .cb { display: inline-block; max-width: 90%; padding: 7px 10px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11.5px; line-height: 1.45; }
    .cb.in { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: rgba(245,239,225,0.85); border-radius: 10px 10px 10px 2px; }
    .cb.out { background: var(--teal); color: var(--navy); border-radius: 10px 10px 2px 10px; float: right; font-weight: 500; }
    .cb.sys { background: rgba(176,139,62,0.15); color: var(--brass); border: 1px solid rgba(176,139,62,0.2); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 10px; display: block; width: 100%; text-align: center; }
    .cm.out-wrap { text-align: right; }

    /* OPERATOR TYPES */
    .operator-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .op-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px 22px; }
    .op-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .op-title { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #F5EFE1; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; }
    .op-desc { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(245,239,225,0.55); line-height: 1.65; }
    .op-wins { margin-top: 14px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
    .op-win { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(245,239,225,0.7); display: flex; gap: 8px; }
    .op-win::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--teal); flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 700; }

    /* LANDLINE */
    .landline-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .ll-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--rule); padding: 24px; }
    .ll-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .ll-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .ll-desc { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(27,26,23,0.6); line-height: 1.65; }
    .ll-flow { margin-top: 14px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
    .ll-step { font-size: 12.5px; color: rgba(27,26,23,0.65); padding-left: 16px; position: relative; }
    .ll-step::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--teal); font-weight: 700; }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-band { background: var(--navy); padding: 80px 0; text-align: center; }
    .cta-band h2 { color: #F5EFE1; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-band p { font-size: 17px; color: rgba(245,239,225,0.55); max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto 36px; }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer { background: #060C12; padding: 28px 0; }
    .footer-row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
    .footer-brand { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(245,239,225,0.6); }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
    .footer-links a { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(245,239,225,0.3); text-decoration: none; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: rgba(245,239,225,0.6); }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .dash-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; height: auto; }
      .dash-detail { display: none; }
      .landline-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="nav-row">
      <a href="/" class="nav-brand">Task<span>Rocket</span></a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/aitha">Aitha for Trades</a>
        <a href="/aitha-pm">Aitha PM</a>
        <a href="/demo">Live Demo</a>
        <a href="https://ruynbnxa5n.zite.so" target="_blank" class="nav-cta">Schedule a demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Aitha PM — Full walkthrough</div>
    <h1>Your tenants call.<br/><em>We handle everything else.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">A complete look at how Aitha PM works — from the moment a tenant calls in to the moment the issue is resolved, documented, and logged. For residential and commercial property managers, large and small.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="https://ruynbnxa5n.zite.so" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">Schedule a demo →</a>
      <a href="/demo" class="btn-ghost">View live dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW A CALL WORKS -->
<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">The core flow</div>
    <h2>From the first ring to<br/>a resolved incident.</h2>
    <p class="lead">Tenants don't download apps. They don't log into portals. They call the number — the same way they'd call any business — and Aitha PM takes it from there.</p>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step-row">
        <div class="step-num-wrap"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-line"></div></div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-title">Tenant calls in</div>
          <div class="step-desc">The tenant calls your property's dedicated phone number. Aitha PM answers. It lets the tenant know they've reached the property management line and asks them to describe what they need. No prompts, no menus, no hold music. Just leave a message.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-row">
        <div class="step-num-wrap"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-line"></div></div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-title">Voicemail transcribed instantly</div>
          <div class="step-desc">The moment the tenant hangs up, Aitha PM transcribes the voicemail. Within seconds the message exists as text the AI can read, reason about, and act on. Whether the tenant called from a cell phone or a landline — the system handles both.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-row">
        <div class="step-num-wrap"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-line"></div></div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-title">AI classifies the issue</div>
          <div class="step-desc">Aitha PM reads the transcription and classifies it in under five seconds. Safety emergency. Information request. Self-fixable maintenance. Vendor-needed maintenance. Each path leads to a different response — immediate, precise, and appropriate to the urgency level.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-row">
        <div class="step-num-wrap"><div class="step-num">4</div><div class="step-line"></div></div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-title">The right response goes out</div>
          <div class="step-desc">The tenant gets a reply — by text if they called from a cell, by callback if they called from a landline. The on-call contact gets notified when and only when human involvement is actually needed. Everything is logged to the dashboard the moment it happens.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOUR PATHS -->
<section class="section-parchment">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Four paths</div>
    <h2>Every call goes somewhere.<br/>Nothing falls through.</h2>
    <p class="lead">The classification determines what happens next. No two calls are treated the same way — because no two calls are the same.</p>
    <div class="paths">
      <div class="path-card red">
        <div class="path-icon">🚨</div>
        <div class="path-title">Safety emergency</div>
        <div class="path-desc">Gas smell, flooding, fire, electrical hazard. Bypasses every queue. The tenant gets emergency instructions immediately. The on-call contact gets a call and a text at the same time. No delay, no approval needed.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="path-card blue">
        <div class="path-icon">📄</div>
        <div class="path-title">Information request</div>
        <div class="path-desc">Lease questions, rent due dates, vacancy inquiries, payment links, move-out procedures, policy questions. AI answers directly from the property's knowledge base. Tenant gets their answer in under a minute. Property manager never has to pick up the phone.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="path-card green">
        <div class="path-icon">🔧</div>
        <div class="path-title">Self-fixable maintenance</div>
        <div class="path-desc">Tripped breaker, clogged drain, running toilet, GFCI reset, AC filter, pilot light. AI asks the tenant if they'd like to try a quick fix. If yes, walks them through it step by step. If it doesn't work — or they decline — the call moves to vendor dispatch automatically.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="path-card amber">
        <div class="path-icon">🏗️</div>
        <div class="path-title">Vendor dispatch</div>
        <div class="path-desc">HVAC failure, major plumbing, electrical, structural. AI identifies the trade needed, texts the on-call contact a numbered vendor list, and dispatches whoever they select — sending the work order, confirming acceptance, and updating the tenant — all without a single phone call from the manager.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DASHBOARD MOCKUP -->
<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">The dashboard</div>
    <h2>One screen.<br/>Every property. Every incident.</h2>
    <p class="lead">Open incidents sorted by urgency. Every tenant, every vendor, every conversation — live, in one place. The property manager opens it in the morning and the night is already documented.</p>

