<!-- LANDLINE -->
<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Landline-aware</div>
    <h2>Cell or landline —<br/>every tenant gets a response.</h2>
    <p class="lead">Most AI tools only handle text-back responses. That leaves out older residential tenants and nearly all commercial tenants who call from an office line. Aitha PM detects how a tenant called and responds accordingly.</p>

    <div class="landline-grid">
      <div class="ll-card">
        <div class="ll-icon">📱</div>
        <div class="ll-title">Cell phone caller</div>
        <div class="ll-desc">The standard flow. Voicemail transcribed, issue triaged, text response sent within 60 seconds. Conversation continues by text until resolved.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ll-card">
        <div class="ll-icon">☎️</div>
        <div class="ll-title">Landline caller</div>
        <div class="ll-desc">Aitha PM detects the landline at the moment the call comes in and routes the response through a professional outbound callback instead.</div>
        <div class="ll-flow">
          <div class="ll-step">Emergency → callback placed immediately, on-call alerted at the same time</div>
          <div class="ll-step">Routine → callback queued for 8am next business morning</div>
          <div class="ll-step">Designated mobile on file → text sent in addition to the callback</div>
          <div class="ll-step">Designated email on file → email sent overnight for routine issues</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

